function Start(idActor, snoQuest)
	actorCloneKiraz = Hydra.CreatePersonalClone(ActorKirazStart)
	if (Hydra.ActorIsValid(actorCloneKiraz)) then
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(actorCloneKiraz, ActorKirazEnd, "NPC_WALK", true)
		Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(actorCloneKiraz, ActorKirazEnd)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(actorCloneKiraz)
	end
end

function Start()
	local idYoncaFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Hawe_S04_YoncaFollower")
	if (Hydra.ActorIsValid(ActorKirazEnd)) and (Hydra.ActorIsValid(idYoncaFollower)) then
		Hydra.ActorPlayDisembodiedConversation(conv_EscortBarkKiraz, idSelf) --disembodied Kiraz bark
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idYoncaFollower, conv_EscortBarkKiraz, true)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_BestowalBark01, idSelf, idYoncaFollower)
	end
end

function Start(snoQuest, idActorFollower)
	--Yonca hangs the first windchime
	local idYoncaFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("NPC_QST_Hawe_S04_YoncaFollower")	
	if (Hydra.ActorIsValid(idYoncaFollower)) then
		Hydra.ActorDisableAI(idYoncaFollower)
		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idYoncaFollower, YoncaGraveChimeLoc, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
		Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(idYoncaFollower, "AnimKey_Use_Phased", 0.5, false)
		Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(idYoncaFollower)
		Hydra.ActorEnableAI(idYoncaFollower)
	end
end
